data.text:
List of notable or famous gymnasts from Canada, with bios and photos, including the top gymnasts born in Canada and even some popular gymnasts who immigrated to Canada. If you're trying to find out the names of famous Canadian gymnasts then this list is the perfect resource for you. These gymnasts are among the most prominent in their field, and information about each well-known gymnast from Canada is included when available.

Use every item on this list for yours, from Kyle Shewfelt to Elyse Hopfner-Hibbs.

This historic gymnasts from Canada list can help answer the questions "Who are some Canadian gymnasts of note?" and "Who are the most famous gymnasts from Canada?" These prominent gymnasts of Canada may or may not be currently alive, but what they all have in common is that they're all respected Canadian gymnasts.

Use this list of renowned Canadian gymnasts to discover some new gymnasts that you aren't familiar with. Don't forget to share this list by clicking one of the social media icons at the top or bottom of the page. {#nodes}
